{"tid":1485701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得叫人走/散就得 唔洗又話割又屌哂老母","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:46:12.000Z","uid":159906,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e03025d15e64a7bd0a96bdadb58e33e7417976","tid":1485701,"uid":159906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"我明白你地都係想大家好 冇手足出事<br />\n今日可以完美結束 <br />\n兄弟可能有做得唔好既地方 可以改善 <br />\n但又唔洗下下割席 問候伯母<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核彈都唔割</span><br />\n<br />\n我只係想大家平平安安返屋企<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"d646c0841c200fa80d119e4e5e3ff58b385cbf1c","tid":1485701,"uid":159906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:29:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc0c802b455a062016237a5d37d80968420a72b1","tid":1485701,"uid":159906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08b2caa013f76687f0ef98f0666f0bda7c9fbb32","tid":1485701,"uid":159906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:30:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e80c8a6afa2cb9e3245df65744458e9f8aa778b","tid":1485701,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"冇大台缺點就係我地未必知道啲係鬼<br />\n如果現場有部份係手足（鬼唔理佢）<br />\n有手足覺得係背叛左今日自己嘅努力<br />\n就請諗返前線手足都做左好大嘅努力<br />\n兄弟爬山，就算做錯野都唔割<br />\n佢地今日可能係破壞左170 萬人嘅努力<br />\n但佢地可以反省，我地都可以包容<br />\n為呢場運動付出代價<br />\n<br />\n致連登所有手足"},{"pid":"247b9aaeb0bf2f6d531582621ac39f604cb9572c","tid":1485701,"uid":159906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:46:12.000Z","msg":"推"}]}